### How to Test Login

> [!TIP]
> **Use a Local Server**: Firebase Authentication often blocks the `file://` protocol. For the best experience, run the app on a local server.
>
> **Already Running**: A python server has been started for you at `http://localhost:8000`.

### Option 1: Email/Password Login

1. Open [http://localhost:8000/index.html](http://localhost:8000/index.html) in your browser
2. If you don't have an account, click "Sign up" to create one
3. Enter your email and password
4. Click "Login"
5. You should be redirected to the passenger dashboard

